org.osgeo.mapguide

Class MgGeometryFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgObject
      • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgDisposable
        • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgGuardDisposable
          • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgGeometryFactory

  • public class MgGeometryFactory
extends MgGuardDisposable
    The MgGeometryFactory class is used to construct objects whose classes are derived from MgGeometry.
